high_descs: Turn left and turn right and head towards the sink
Pick up the lettuce that is on the counter next to the sink
Turn around and head towards the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door and put the lettuce inside
Pick up the lettuce that is on the table
Turn around and head towards the refrigerator
Walk to the refrigerator
When you get to the refrigerator open the refrigerator door and put the lettuce inside and then close the refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Take the heads of lettuce, put them in the refrigerator, shut the refrigerator door

high_descs: Turn right walk towards sink
Pick up lettuce from counter
Turn right, walk to fridge
Put lettuce on top shelf of fridge
Turn around, walk to table
Pick up lettuce from table
Turn around, walk to fridge
Put lettuce on top shelf of fridge
anns.task_desc: Retrieve two heads of lettuce, place on top shelf of fridge

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove, then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce next to the toaster.
Move slightly away from the counter, then turn right at walk to the door.  Turn left so you are facing the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the head of lettuce on the right side of the top shelf, and close the refrigerator.
Turn completely around, walk to the wall, turn right to face the table.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the table.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the head of lettuce on the left side of the top shelf, and close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put both heads of lettuce in the refrigerator.
